OL,3,CHospitals in NI in 'perpetual cycle of
OL,4,Ccrisis'
OL,6,FHospitals in Northern Ireland,
OL,7,Faccording to the Royal College of
OL,8,FEmergency Medicine (RECM), are in a
OL,9,F"perpetual cycle of crisis".
OL,11,FThe crisis is costing lives with
OL,12,Ftargets being missed continuously,
OL,13,Fwhile the death toll continues to rise
OL,14,Fdue to prolonged waiting times.
OL,16,FGiving evidence to Stormont's Health
OL,17,FCommittee earlier, the RCEM warned
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland is worse off.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
