CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779991869
OL,3,CHospitals in NI in 'perpetual cycle of
OL,4,Ccrisis'
OL,6,FDr Michael Perry, Royal College of
OL,7,FEmergency Medicine said: "On Tuesday
OL,8,Fmorning, we had 326 patients in our
OL,9,FEDs who are waiting a hospital bed.
OL,11,F"We had 327 patients who had been in
OL,12,Four departments over 12 hours.
OL,14,F"As you may have heard of the national
OL,15,F4-hour target, where 95% of patients
OL,16,Fare to be assessed, treated,
OL,17,Fdischarged, or admitted is 95%.
OL,19,F"Our performance for the week across
OL,20,Fthe region between the 8th and 14th of
OL,21,FMay was 36%."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779991869
OL,3,CHospitals in NI in 'perpetual cycle of
OL,4,Ccrisis'
OL,6,FMeanwhile deputy Chair of the Health
OL,7,FCommittee, the Alliance MLA Danny
OL,8,FDonnelly said: "6,323 excess deaths in
OL,9,Fthe last 10 years, and the last 3
OL,10,Fyears over 1,000 excess deaths because
OL,11,Fof those over-long waits in ED.
OL,13,F"You know that these are flashing red
OL,14,Falarm bells that really should be
OL,15,Fscreaming at us that it is a systemic
OL,16,Fissue, and it does require a systemic
OL,17,Fchange."
OL,19,FDr Michael Perry continued: "The
OL,20,Fnational news of fatigue, emergency
OL,21,Fdepartments in crisis is perpetual.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1779991869
OL,3,CHospitals in NI in 'perpetual cycle of
OL,4,Ccrisis'
OL,6,F"I don't want us to fall into the trap
OL,7,Fof thinking this is the same
OL,8,Feverywhere.
OL,10,F"We are in a worse situation than the
OL,11,Frest of the devolved nations and, and,
OL,12,Fand the rest of the UK."
OL,14,FMeanwhile the Health Minister Mike
OL,15,FNesbitt has confirmed #80million will
OL,16,Fbe used to tackle waiting lists this
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
